The original season of The Bad Girls Club (BGC) is perhaps the most overlooked season of all time but that doesn't mean they shouldn't get the recognition they deserve. After all, they did revolutionise the franchise into 16 following seasons. The original castmates were Zara, Leslie, Ripsi, Kerry, Aimee, Jodie & Ty. Ripsi was the first to be kicked off the show and was replaced by DeAnn. Ty was the second to be kicked off and Leslie quit not long after which resulted in them being replaced by Joanna and Andrea. The drama wasn't as extreme as later seasons as the purpose was to actually change into a grown, mature woman.

No copyright intended.
